    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台恶意占库存细则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1269568764492517376",
    "content": "<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">尊敬的商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">您好，为适应业务发展要求，现需对《京东开放平台恶意占库存细则》及其关联规则进行调整</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年8月22日- 2025年8月28日，规则预计于2025年8月29日生效，公示期满后平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\"><strong>原规则链接</strong>：<a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1206154529616302080\">https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1206154529616302080</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\"><strong>核心调整点</strong>：对恶意占库存的范围进行调整，增加多次或多量超出非自用需求下单但不收货的形式。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">调整内容如下：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">一、<a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1206154529616302080\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">《京东开放平台恶意占库存细则》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【违规定义】</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span class=\"16\"><s><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.1</span></s></span><span class=\"16\"><s><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">恶意占库存：</span></s></span><s><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家通过包括但不限于超出合理需求大量下单平台上商品后不付款或使用后款方式支付等，干扰消费者购物权益或其他商家权益，损害正常经营秩序的行为。</span></s></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: 115%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1</span></span><span class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">恶意占库存：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家在平台多次或多量超出非自用需求下单但不付款或不收货的形式干扰消费者购物权益或其他商家权益，损害平台正常经营秩序的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【规则解读】</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span class=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家恶意占库存，包括哪些情形？</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家恶意占库存包括但不限于以下情形：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><s><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（1）商家涉嫌使用其账号、相关联账号、所控制账号或者雇佣他人进行恶意下单不付款或使用后款方式支付的行为；</span></s></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><s><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（2）一次大量下单或多次下单累积商品数量较多不付款或使用后款方式支付的行为；</span></s></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><s><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（3）其他方式进行恶意下单不付款或使用后款方式支付占库存的行为。</span></s></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #e03e2d;\">（1）商家涉嫌使用其账号、相关联账号、所控制账号或者雇佣他人进行占库存行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #e03e2d;\">（2）通过一次性大量下单或多次下单累计商品数量较多，并通过不支付、取消订单、拒收或延迟收货等手段恶意占库存的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">二、<a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=2754#heading-8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》</a></span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第七类 交易作弊</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家在平台多次或多量超出非自用需求下单但不付款或不收货的形式干扰消费者购物权益或其他商家权益，损害平台正常经营秩序的行为。京东有权视商家违规程度且不基于违规次数，对涉事商家、店铺及关联店铺采取包括但不限于违规商品下架、禁止发布新商品、禁止上架待售商品、禁止投放或提报活动、禁止投放或播放广告、品牌停用和限制申请品牌、类目停用和限制开通类目、搜索降权、推荐降权、全店商品下架、降低店铺综合体验分、屏蔽降权、账户止付、定额冻结、提高涉事店铺应缴保证金金额、延长结算周期、扣收保收金、扣收违约金、扣收商家在平台上的近一年内收入、执行店铺清退等措施，同时，不基于违规次数，京东有权对商家的关联方或关联店铺采取一项或多项的管控措施，具体管控措施详见</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #e03e2d;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=4680&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><span class=\"15\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台关联店铺管理规则》</span></span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</p>",
